WEBVTT

00:00:13.325 --> 00:00:20.124 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Noah walked with Jehovah;
he was pleasing in God’s eyes.

00:00:20.124 --> 00:00:27.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He stuck close to his family;
they wanted to do what’s right.

00:00:27.381 --> 00:00:34.638 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They worked hard to build an ark
to save them from the Flood.

00:00:34.638 --> 00:00:42.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They listened to Jehovah,
and they preached to ev’ryone.

00:00:42.104 --> 00:00:51.363 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Noah was faithful to Jehovah,
And as the Flood got closer,

00:00:51.363 --> 00:00:56.452 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He preached until the end.

00:00:56.452 --> 00:01:06.003 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If I try to be like Noah,
Faithful to Jehovah,

00:01:06.003 --> 00:01:09.673 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I can be God’s friend.

00:01:13.427 --> 00:01:20.100 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When they went out preaching,
there were people who made fun.

00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:27.441 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But Noah kept his fam’ly safe
until the work was done.

00:01:27.441 --> 00:01:34.698 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Even though the world around them
was violent and bad,

00:01:34.698 --> 00:01:42.373 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They endured and they found joy;
they made Jehovah glad.

00:01:42.373 --> 00:01:51.382 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Noah was faithful to Jehovah,
And as the Flood got closer,

00:01:51.382 --> 00:01:55.260 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He preached until the end.

00:01:56.762 --> 00:02:05.813 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If I try to be like Noah,
Faithful to Jehovah,

00:02:05.813 --> 00:02:09.400 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I can be God’s friend.

